OL,6,FJohn Swinney must "make amends" to the
OL,7,FCovid bereaved for deleting key
OL,8,FWhatsApp messages if he is to become
OL,9,FScotland's next first minister, the
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats have said.
OL,12,FThe former deputy first minister is
OL,13,Fthe likely candidate to replace Humza
OL,14,FYousaf in the top job next week after
OL,15,Fothers ruled themselves out of the
OL,16,Fcontest.
