OL,3,CSwinney told to 'make amends' to Covid
OL,4,Cbereaved if he becomes first minister
OL,6,FHowever, Scottish Liberal Democrat
OL,7,Fleader Alex Cole-Hamilton has told the
OL,8,FPerthshire North MSP, who served as
OL,9,FNicola Sturgeon's deputy during the
OL,10,Fpandemic, to "overhaul government
OL,11,Ftransparency" if he is selected for
OL,12,Fthe role.
OL,14,FIn January, Mr Swinney admitted to the
OL,15,FUK Covid-19 Inquiry that he "manually"
OL,16,Fdeleted informal messages between
OL,17,Fhimself and Ms Sturgeon in accordance
OL,18,Fwith Scottish Government guidance.
