OL,6,FThe Scottish Government has since said
OL,7,Fit is committed to learning lessons,
OL,8,Fwith a review into the use of WhatsApp
OL,9,Fand other communications announced.
OL,11,FHowever, Mr Cole-Hamilton has said:
OL,12,F"When he set out his leadership bid
OL,13,Fearlier this week, John Swinney said
OL,14,Fthat his values are based on helping
OL,15,Fsome of the most vulnerable people in
OL,16,Four society. If he is serious about
OL,17,Fthat then he must make amends to all
OL,18,Fthose whose lives were ripped apart by
OL,19,FCovid.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
