OL,3,CSwinney told to 'make amends' to Covid
OL,4,Cbereaved if he becomes first minister
OL,6,F"It was John Swinney who deleted his
OL,7,Fpandemic messages, alongside Nicola
OL,8,FSturgeon and other members of her top
OL,9,Fteam. By doing so, they undermined the
OL,10,Fwork of both the UK and Scottish Covid
OL,11,Finquiries and deprived all those who
OL,12,Flost loved ones of the answers and
OL,13,Funderstanding they are searching for.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
