OL,6,FA spokesman for Mr Swinney said: "Mr
OL,7,FSwinney's deepest sympathies are with
OL,8,Fall those who lost loved ones during
OL,9,Fthe pandemic.
OL,11,F"Mr Swinney addressed the subject of
OL,12,Fmessage retention during an extensive
OL,13,Fevidence session at the Covid Inquiry.
OL,14,FWhile giving evidence, Mr Swinney made
OL,15,Fclear that he acted in-line with the
OL,16,Fexisting Scottish Government policy at
OL,17,Fthat point in time."
